1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,120
It's a strange reality.

2
00:00:02,120 --> 00:00:05,200
Your body's atoms are ancient starlight,

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:07,720
a profound truth often missed.

4
00:00:07,720 --> 00:00:11,720
Each element forged in distant dying suns,

5
00:00:11,720 --> 00:00:14,040
