6
00:00:14,040 --> 00:00:16,520
You are the universe, briefly aware,

7
00:00:16,520 --> 00:00:20,120
experiencing its own intricate fleeting form.

8
00:00:20,120 --> 00:00:24,960
This cosmic lineage reveals you are not separate.

9
00:00:24,960 --> 00:00:27,640
You are its conscious breath.

10
00:00:27,640 --> 00:00:32,640
Its conscious breath, a profound truth often missed.

